title: Panamax Power360 Power Strip Overview
description:
Panamax Power360  8-Outlet Power Strip - P360-8 - http://abt.com/product/88833/Panamax-P3608.html

Best for Media Rooms. Two detachable USB modules tether to table or desktop for convenient USB charging hub (6 cable included). Features best in class protection with active over/under-voltage protection that automatically resets itself when power conditions return to normal. The Circle of Protection™ LED displays real time protection wiring and voltage status. The Power360-8 is covered by a lifetime product warranty plus a 500000 connected equipment protection policy.
Features:
• 8 Protected AC Outlets
• 2 dual-port USB modules
• Protect-or-Disconnect
• SmartGuard
• Circle of Protection
• Signal Line Protection
• Lifetime Warranty
